extends layout

block content
    h1= title
    p Welcome to #{title}

    button#buttonGetJson Parse Json
    button#buttonGetJsonAjax Get Json with Ajax
    button#buttonGetMarkdown Parse Markdown

    p#debug

    div#radioDiv

    div
        pre#markdown

    p Look in routes/users.js to see why these urls response as they do.

    ul
        li.button
            a(href="/") /root
        li.button
            a(href="/users/") /users
        li.button
            a(href="/users/a") /users/a
        li.button
            a(href="/users/acat") /users/acat
        li.button
            a(href="/users/bar") /users/bar

    p#response
    p#route
    p#result
    p#request
    p#params

    ul#display

    :markdown
        Docs on routing found [here](http://expressjs.com/guide/routing.html).

